Package suncertify.exception

Exception Summary
InvalidModeSelectedException This handles Exception when an Invalid Mode is Selected when trying to run the program from the command line with argument(s) other than the single mode flag or the one that this application support
URLyBirdException This extends Exception class so that other exceptions in this project can extend this and be its sub class
